HEADWORD: Insurrectionary
<hw>In`sur*rec"tion*a*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Pertaining to, or characterized by, insurrection; rebellious;
seditious.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Their murderous <qex>insurrectionary</qex> system.</q>
<rj><qau>Burke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Insurrectionist</ent>⟦br⟧
